				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Beastlord/Chanter combo can be quite deadly.  Forget the fact that both classes have a mana regen buff.  Well, don't forget it, just push it aside for a moment and consider this.  I had a mage that i used to group with my chanter buddy, and his sword/shield pet was damn near useless.  It always held agro over any pet I summoned even when my pet was a higher lvl than his.  With my beastlord and his chanter we have no such problem.  Unlike my elemental pet from before, our animals proc and increase the hate the mob has for us/them significantly.  The chanter pet can't keep up, so doesn't get hit.  End result, chanter pet DPS w/o the chanter losing his pet all the time.  Basiclly our pets are MT's with our outstanding heals to back them up, and the chanters sword/shield happily does damage without drawing the mobs attention at all.  Great combo, really makes the chanter pet shine!!  
<br />

