				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've been playing a friend's chanter the last couple days to get him caught back up to my BL.  WOW is all i can really say.  I grinded him through lvl 41 in about 2 hours in EW.  Charm an ulthok manowar and parade it around killing its little walrus friends.  It can kill about 6 of em before charm breaks usually.  And by then, its below 20% so it walks away and one nuke kills it.  Chanters are insanely powerful.
