When we group, we usually pull a similar trick.  I tell pet not to taunt, chanter grabs a pet, we run around killing stuff until pet breaks.  When pet breaks, my pet tanks the target (it already has aggro), and I FoL the former charmed mob for chanter to regain control.  Fun fun <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
