				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I also use Rune of Z as a means to slow dmg to my Beastlord. If you're hunting somewhere that drops gems, you'll still come out with a profit even after burning through a stack of Peridots. 
<br />

<br />
And 2-boxing a beast/chanter is like playing a multi-class character in other RPG games. YOu get the best of two classes! I love being able to single pull in places a Beastlord would not normally do that (using pacification), and the mana regen is suitable for non-stop action almost anywhere!
<br />

<br />
All I have to do before heading out is find an uber chanter to cast longest lasting virtue on me, and my two toons can do quite a bit in a short period of time.<br />_________________<br /><font size=3><b>Elder <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=109966>Ssmellycat Meowington</a></b> - <i> Feral Lord</i></font>
